</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='351841' id='t-351841'>So my question now to you is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354255' id='t-354255'>well, it's a nice solution,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356000' id='t-356000'>it's very accessible, it's safe.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='358130' id='t-358130'>What would you use it for?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='359671' id='t-359671'>What would you use such a camera for in your life?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
